The French newspaper Le Monde claims that the November 13, 2015 Paris attacks were coordinated from Belgium by a single unidentified suspect. (Lemonde.fr)For the first time, Russia strikes Islamic State targets in northern Syria with 3M-54 Klub (Kalibr) cruise missiles launched from a Kilo-class submarine in the Mediterranean, according to the Russian Minister of Defence, Sergey Shoygu. (RT)